TITLE: React Implementation of Hide Middleware
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to implement the hide middleware in React components using the useFloating hook.
SOURCE: https://github.com/floating-ui/floating-ui/blob/master/website/pages/docs/hide.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const {refs, floatingStyles, middlewareData} = useFloating({
  middleware: [hide()],
});

return (
  <div
    ref={refs.setFloating}
    style={{
      ...floatingStyles,
      visibility: middlewareData.hide?.referenceHidden
        ? 'hidden'
        : 'visible',
    }}
  />
);
